<feed xml:lang="en" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>边缘 - 所有帖子</title><icon>https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/community_logos/52801/VER_Logomark_32x32..png</icon><updated> 2024-09-18T15:13:21-04:00</updated><id> https://www.theverge.com/rss/full.xml</id><link href="https://www.theverge.com/" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><entry><published> 2024-09-18T15:13:21-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-18T15:13:21-04:00</updated><title> Substack 正试图将其作家变成主播</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Substack 实时视频功能的屏幕截图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/eEUYogzKnBzUlj6G9p_GshXw8Ek=/450x0:5310x3240/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73594439/ec475ce2_114e_48c1_bb9a _ad3a96654ec4_5760x3240.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Substack&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;BE6uwW&quot;>;Substack 现在允许创作者串流直播视频，作为与观众联系的另一种方式。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;GyisRH&quot;>;Substack 从新闻通讯平台的基础上不断扩展，包括添加 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/4/11/23677946 /substack-notes-twitter-throttled-blocked-links&quot;>;类似 Twitter 的 Notes 帖子&lt;/a>; 以及 &lt;a href=&quot;https://on.substack.com/p/video-on-substack-升级&quot;>;发布视频播客&lt;/a>;，甚至让人们&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/8/14/23832321/substack-follow-writers-button&quot;>;关注其他用户，而无需订阅它们&lt;/a>;。截至上个月，您&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/8/24216317/substack-socia-media-newsletter-creators&quot;>;甚至不需要&lt;/a>;建立一个出版物来分享内容。通过直播视频，创作者将能够与粉丝实时互动，而无需依赖 Twitch 等其他平台。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;EIKMuf&quot;>;当您上线时，您的订阅者将立即收到通知，您可以将您的视频流提供给所有人、所有订阅者或仅付费订阅者，&lt;a href=&quot;https://on.substack.com/p/introducing-live-video-in-the-substack&quot;>;根据博客...&lt;/a>;&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/18/24248308/substack-live-video&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip ;&lt;/a>;&lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/18/24248308/substack-live-video" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/18/24248308/substack-live-video</id><author><name>杰·彼得斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-18T14:31:56-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-18T14:31:56-04:00</updated><title>最好的预算机器人真空吸尘器</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;各种扫地机器人插图&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/HibcNT_fQEjjbn2ocPGsJMt6h-E=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/ uploads/chorus_image/image/72624795/Best_Robot_vaccum_cleaners_01.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;插图：The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;您不必花一大笔钱让机器人清洁您的地板。这是我们精选的您现在可以购买的最具成本效益的机器人。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23846479/best-budget-robot-vacuum-robot-拖把&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23846479/best-budget-robot-vacuum-robot-mop" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23846479/best-budget-robot-vacuum-robot-mop</id><author><name>詹妮弗·帕蒂森·图伊</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-18T14:04:20-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-18T14:04:20-04:00</updated><title> HTC 推出具有色彩直通功能且专注于游戏的 Vive Focus Vision</title><content type="html"> &lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;一个人在室内佩戴 HTC Focus Vision。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/jejJmUYHuo8qZ_QwWDeRtHJMsEM=/0x88:3595x2485/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73594287/Vive_Focus_Vision_closeup.0.png&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;Focus Vision 看起来有点混乱！&lt;/em>; |图片：HTC&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;avAPdZ&quot;>;HTC 有 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/htc-vive-launches-vive-focus- vision-xr-headset-for-enterprises-and-high-end-gaming-302251269.html&quot;>;宣布&lt;/a>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs= 1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vive.com%2Fus%2Fproduct%2Fvive-focus-vision%2Foverview%2F&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com% 2F2024%2F9%2F18%2F24248052%2Fhtc-vive-focus-vision-vr-headset-eye-tracking-color-passthrough-preorder&quot; rel=&quot;Recommended nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Vive Focus Vision&lt;/a>; ，一款基于 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/22588917/htc-vive-focus-3-vr-headset-review&quot;>;Vive Focus 3&lt;/a>; 构建的新型 VR 耳机，具有以下功能例如颜色直通和更好的 PC 网络共享支持。售价 999 美元的 Focus Vision 从即日起至 10 月 17 日可在 HTC 网站上预订。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;o7vuEn&quot;>;Focus Vision 既可以作为独立设备使用，也可以通过 USB-C 连接到您的 PC。它本质上是该公司于 2021 年发布的 Focus 3 的增强版 - 它具有相同的每眼分辨率 2448 x 2448 和 120 度视野，并且还使用 Snapdragon XR2 芯片。但它获得了双 16MP 摄像头和彩色直通等功能，并且现在可以自动调整镜头以补偿眼睛之间的距离。 &lt;/p>; &lt;div id=&quot;P3ac0u&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;gallery:12429609&quot;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;PksriC&quot;>;HTC 面向游戏玩家... &lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/18/24248052/htc-vive-focus-vision-vr-headset-eye-tracking-color-passthrough-预购&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/18/24248052/htc-vive-focus-vision-vr-headset-eye-tracking-color-passthrough-preorder" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/18/24248052/htc-vive-focus-vision-vr-headset-eye-tracking-color-passthrough-preorder</id><author><name>韦斯·戴维斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-18T13:55:46-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-18T13:55:46-04:00</updated><title> YouTube 正在添加“季节”，让您喜爱的频道更像 Netflix</title><content type="html"> &lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;抽象背景上的 YouTube 徽标&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/U20PRhsAF8cDTjdHLtfmJqjb4FQ=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads /chorus_image/image/73594237/acastro_STK092_02.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;插图：Alex Castro / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;stFhmG&quot;>;YouTube 创作者现在可以将他们的视频分成不同的 &lt;a href=&quot;https://blog.youtube/news-and-events/made-on-youtube-2024/#:~:text=Unlocking%20more%20opportunities%20in%20the%20living%20room%3A&quot; >;季节和剧集&lt;/a>;，让观众更轻松地在电视上浏览并连续观看。即将推出的功能正值 YouTube 越来越多地进军客厅之际，据该公司称，电视上的 YouTuber 收入同比增长了 30%。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;13MfPk&quot;>;内容创作者很快就可以定制自己的内容以与在电视上观看时看起来与 Netflix 和其他流媒体服务非常相似的格式向观众上传内容，并提供全屏剧集描述以及可供导航的季节和剧集层次结构。&lt;/p>; &lt;figure class=&quot;e-image &quot;>; &lt;cite>;GIF：谷歌&lt;/cite>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;lE6QVh&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot; readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;YouTube Hype 为小型创作者提供了发光的地方&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024 /9/18/24247995/youtube-hype-creators&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;YouTube 社区就像创作者的迷你 Discord&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/ 18/24247529/youtube-communities-social-comments&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;QxC9rs&quot;>;YouTube 尚未说明新格式将如何转换为桌面和移动用户界面，但希望在所有平台上都能以某种形式看到它...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/18/24248206/youtube-season- Episode-format-organizing-tv-netflix-binge&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/18/24248206/youtube-season-episode-format-organizing-tv-netflix-binge" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/18/24248206/youtube-season-episode-format-organizing-tv-netflix-binge</id><author><name>奥马尔·沙基尔</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-18T13:02:46-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-18T13:02:46-04:00</updated><title>狮门影业签署协议在其电影和节目中训练人工智能模型</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;一个穿着黑色西装外套的男人坐在一个穿着飘逸的白色托加长袍、戴着金色月桂花环的人旁边。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/7sJKqnfyk_HyTktGxzIyF4cUeNo=/513x0:3584x2047/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73594143/mega_04_11_43_07_00 362479rc.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;来自狮门影业即将上映的影片之一《特大城市》的场景。&lt;/em>; |图片：Lionsgate&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;9z8opM&quot;>;AI 初创公司 Runway 有 &lt;a href=&quot;h